{
  "stem": "802.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if they did, they fell into the river and often drowned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So this was a means of punishment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Here, too, there were no gas chambers, just, you know, shootings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother, sister, and I, again, tried to be inseparable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My cousins, also-- the two male cousins-- were transported to the same camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And at one point, my mother really looked just absolutely terrible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was an SS man who ran the factory-- the plant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he decided that he wanted to send my mother to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Not on camp-- the campgrounds-- because there wasn't any.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But just to send her away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my cousin intervened, because he was a jeweler.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he was making-- he was making jewelery for the Germans who were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So he had certain privileges.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the next day, this SS man, we used to call him Totenkopf, which means 'death head.' You know, they used to wear these, uh-- death-- you know, the head-- the skeletal symbol-- so.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So when he saw my mother, he was enraged, and he beat her terribly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But there was no other transport going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then, of course, the starvation was pretty much the same.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I mean, it's unspeakable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then, we heard rumors that the Russians were not too far away and that the war was coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we're pleading with God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We're praying to God to send bombs-- even if the bombs were to kill us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So every time we heard something that sounded like a bomb, we're very happy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Then they-- the Germans did not want to leave any-- any, um-- traces behind them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So they were going to transport us to Germany, in trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So the trains were prepared for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
